{"id":14935,"date":"2023-12-01T16:33:51","date_gmt":"2023-12-01T09:33:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=14935"},"modified":"2023-12-01T16:36:36","modified_gmt":"2023-12-01T09:36:36","slug":"suv-do-thi-hyundai-creta-bat-ngo-len-dong-vuot-mat-bo-doi-kia-sonet-seltos","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/suv-do-thi-hyundai-creta-bat-ngo-len-dong-vuot-mat-bo-doi-kia-sonet-seltos\/","title":{"rendered":"SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb: Hyundai Creta b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd &#8216;l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng&#8217;, v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kia Sonet, Seltos"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2 class=\"detail-sapo\" data-role=\"sapo\">L\u01b0\u1ee3ng xe b\u00e1n ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh, v\u01b0\u1ee3t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng 1.200 chi\u1ebfc gi\u00fap Hyundai Creta v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng doanh s\u1ed1 SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, sau th\u1eddi gian kh\u00e1 d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe Kia hay Toyota l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt.<\/h2>\n<div id=\"zone-k911czvz\">\n<div id=\"share-k911czwh\">\n<div id=\"placement-kan969mf\">\n<div id=\"banner-k911czvz-kan969mq\">\n<div id=\"slot-1-k911czvz-kan969mq\">\n<div id=\"ssppagebid_6324\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"detail-cmain\">\n<div class=\"detail-content afcbc-body\" data-role=\"content\" data-io-article-url=\"https:\/\/thanhnien.vn\/suv-do-thi-hyundai-creta-bat-ngo-len-dong-vuot-mat-bo-doi-kia-sonet-seltos-18523112213245653.htm\">\n<div data-check-position=\"body_start\"><\/div>\n<p>Trong m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng m\u00e0 to\u00e0n th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 t\u00f4 vi\u1ec7t nam b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i, SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fa \u00fd, khi l\u00e0 ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe hi\u1ebfm hoi ghi nh\u1eadn doanh s\u1ed1 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng.<\/p>\n<p>C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, theo s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n \u00f4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0v\u00e0 TC Motor &#8211; \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng xe Hyundai t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb sau th\u00e1ng 9 \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3m \u0111i\u1ec3m, b\u01b0\u1edbc sang th\u00e1ng 10.2023 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng xe b\u00e1n ra \u0111\u1ea1t x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 5.000 xe; t\u0103ng h\u01a1n 600 xe, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea7n 15%.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"Doanh s\u1ed1 SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00e1ng 10.2023\" href=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-xe-thanhnien-1700633941610342669444.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" id=\"img_651668778430738432\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb: Hyundai Creta b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd 'l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng', v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kia Sonet\/Seltos - \u1ea2nh 1.\" src=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/thumb_w\/640\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-xe-thanhnien-1700633941610342669444.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/thumb_w\/640\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-xe-thanhnien-1700633941610342669444.jpg 1x,https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-xe-thanhnien-1700633941610342669444.jpg 2x\" alt=\"SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb: Hyundai Creta b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd 'l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng', v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kia Sonet\/Seltos - \u1ea2nh 1.\" width=\"1293\" height=\"905\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-xe-thanhnien-1700633941610342669444.jpg\" data-adbro-processed=\"true\" \/><\/a><\/div><figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"Nh\u1eadp ch\u00fa th\u00edch \u1ea3nh\">Doanh s\u1ed1 SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00e1ng 10.2023<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Toyota RAnze , t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe \u0111ang ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 doanh s\u1ed1 (g\u1ed3m Kia Sonet, Kia Seltos, Toyota Corolla Cross, Hyundai Creta, Honda HR-V, Mazda CX-3, Mazda CX-30 v\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh Toyota Yaris Corrs \u0111\u1ec1u ghi nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3ng xe \u0111\u1ebfn tay kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u0103ng. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Hyundai Creta.<\/p>\n<p>Sau nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng gi\u1eefa n\u0103m 2023 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t &#8220;phong \u0111\u1ed9&#8221;, m\u1eabu xe H\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh nh\u1edd h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t tri\u1ec3n khai. \u1ede hai th\u00e1ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Creta li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea1t doanh s\u1ed1 cao, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 th\u00e1ng 10 v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi 1.235 xe b\u00e0n giao t\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 3, m\u1eabu\u00a0 xe h\u00e0n m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i ghi nh\u1eadn doanh s\u1ed1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng 1.000 xe\/th\u00e1ng.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"Hyundai Creta c\u00f3 th\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp &quot;t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng&quot;, khi \u0111\u1ea1t doanh s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean 1.200 xe\" href=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-1-xe-thanhnien-17006339415261474272765.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" id=\"img_651668774627004416\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb: Hyundai Creta b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd 'l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng', v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kia Sonet\/Seltos - \u1ea2nh 2.\" src=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/thumb_w\/640\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-1-xe-thanhnien-17006339415261474272765.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/thumb_w\/640\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-1-xe-thanhnien-17006339415261474272765.jpg 1x,https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-1-xe-thanhnien-17006339415261474272765.jpg 2x\" alt=\"SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb: Hyundai Creta b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd 'l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng', v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kia Sonet\/Seltos - \u1ea2nh 2.\" width=\"864\" height=\"570\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-1-xe-thanhnien-17006339415261474272765.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div><figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"Nh\u1eadp ch\u00fa th\u00edch \u1ea3nh\">Hyundai Creta c\u00f3 th\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp &#8220;t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng&#8221;, khi \u0111\u1ea1t doanh s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean 1.200 xe<\/p>\n<\/figcaption><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Author\">\n<p class=\"\" data-placeholder=\"Nh\u1eadp t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3\">\u0110\u00ecnh Tuy\u00ean<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<p>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Hyundai Creta v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua doanh s\u1ed1 th\u00e1ng \u1edf ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac. B\u1edfi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kia Sonet v\u00e0 Seltos trong th\u00e1ng 10 d\u00f9 v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u00e1n ra 1.152 xe v\u00e0 1.091 xe.<\/p>\n<p>Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Toyota Corolla Cross th\u1eddi gian qua \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd &#8220;\u0111u\u1ed1i s\u1ee9c&#8221; khi doanh s\u1ed1 m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i tr\u0103m xe. Th\u00e1ng qua, m\u1eabu xe Nh\u1eadt tuy c\u00f3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eb9 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 giao \u0111\u1ebfn tay kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng 317 xe, k\u00e9m c\u1ea3 m\u1eabu xe &#8220;\u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng&#8221; Honda HR-V (365 xe).<\/p>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"Toyota Corolla Cross b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd sa s\u00fat \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t\" href=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-2-xe-thanhnien-170063394148528390300.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" id=\"img_651668774537957376\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb: Hyundai Creta b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd 'l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng', v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kia Sonet\/Seltos - \u1ea2nh 3.\" src=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/thumb_w\/640\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-2-xe-thanhnien-170063394148528390300.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/thumb_w\/640\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-2-xe-thanhnien-170063394148528390300.jpg 1x,https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-2-xe-thanhnien-170063394148528390300.jpg 2x\" alt=\"SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb: Hyundai Creta b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd 'l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng', v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kia Sonet\/Seltos - \u1ea2nh 3.\" width=\"1326\" height=\"820\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-2-xe-thanhnien-170063394148528390300.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div><figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"Nh\u1eadp ch\u00fa th\u00edch \u1ea3nh\">Toyota Corolla Cross b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd sa s\u00fat \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t<\/p>\n<\/figcaption><div class=\"PhotoCMS_Author\"><\/div>\n<\/figure>\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n \u1edf b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng doanh s\u1ed1 th\u00e1ng; s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Hyundai Creta, \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a mua s\u1eafm cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m c\u00f2n &#8220;h\u00e2m n\u00f3ng&#8221; cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u0103m 2023 \u1edf ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<p>S\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng cho th\u1ea5y, v\u1edbi hai th\u00e1ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y li\u00ean t\u1ee5c &#8220;t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng&#8221;, m\u1eabu xe nh\u00e0 Hyundai hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t doanh s\u1ed1 l\u0169y k\u1ebf h\u01a1n 7.500 xe. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y v\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u1ea3 Kia Seltos (7.334 xe) v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m qu\u00e1 xa so v\u1edbi hai m\u1eabu xe x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean l\u00e0 Kia Sonet\u00a0(8.808 xe) v\u00e0 Toyota Corolla Cross (9.707 xe). V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 duy tr\u00ec &#8220;phong \u0111\u1ed9&#8221; nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Creta l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<div id=\"zone-l2srqb41\">\n<div id=\"share-l2srqbkq\">\n<div id=\"placement-kspipz1y\">\n<div id=\"banner-l2srqb41-kspiq11b\">\n<div id=\"slot-1-l2srqb41-kspiq11b\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"Xe H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt tr\u01b0\u1edbc xe Nh\u1eadt \u1edf ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" href=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-3-xe-thanhnien-17006339415581406784942.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" id=\"img_651668774586236928\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb: Hyundai Creta b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd 'l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng', v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kia Sonet\/Seltos - \u1ea2nh 4.\" src=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/thumb_w\/640\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-3-xe-thanhnien-17006339415581406784942.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/thumb_w\/640\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-3-xe-thanhnien-17006339415581406784942.jpg 1x,https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-3-xe-thanhnien-17006339415581406784942.jpg 2x\" alt=\"SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb: Hyundai Creta b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd 'l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng', v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kia Sonet\/Seltos - \u1ea2nh 4.\" width=\"1144\" height=\"860\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/images2.thanhnien.vn\/528068263637045248\/2023\/11\/22\/suv-do-thi-thang-10-2023-3-xe-thanhnien-17006339415581406784942.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div><figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"Nh\u1eadp ch\u00fa th\u00edch \u1ea3nh\">Xe H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt tr\u01b0\u1edbc xe Nh\u1eadt \u1edf ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/p>\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<div class=\"dable_placeholder\">\n<div id=\"dablewidget_QXedqQel\" data-widget_id=\"QXedqQel\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, x\u00e9t \u1edf g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y, xe H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u01b0u \u00e1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng Vi\u1ec7t. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi 3 m\u1eabu xe, g\u1ed3m b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i xe Kia (Sonet, Seltos) v\u00e0 Hyundai Creta, c\u00e1c h\u00e3ng xe H\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 &#8220;\u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o&#8221; nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt b\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 Toyota Honda hay Mazda; khi chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u1ebfn 55% th\u1ecb ph\u1ea7n.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i khi nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe Hyundai hay Kia s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn nh\u1edd thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf tr\u1ebb trung, h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tr\u1ebb. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n v\u00e0 trang b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a xe H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt.<\/p>\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>L\u01b0\u1ee3ng xe b\u00e1n ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh, v\u01b0\u1ee3t ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng 1.200 chi\u1ebfc gi\u00fap Hyundai Creta v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng doanh s\u1ed1 SUV \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, sau th\u1eddi gian kh\u00e1 